title: Splash Spray, 2025 New Upgrade Stove Splash Foam Cleaner, Multipurpose Handheld Kitchen Spray for Kitchen, Cabinet, Countertops, Ovens (1 Pcs)
features: 【Powerful Degreaser – Spray & Clean Stubborn Grease】：Our Spray Splash Cleaner is specially formulated to quickly dissolve tough grease and grime. Ideal for high-oil areas like range hoods, exhaust fans, stovetops, and more — making kitchen cleaning easier than ever.

【Premium Formula – Gentle Yet Highly Effective】：Splash Spray Infused with a concentrated yet gentle cleaning formula that emulsifies grease on contact, generating rich foam that lifts dirt without damaging your stovetop or other kitchen surfaces.

【Smart No-Rinse Design – Convenient & Efficient】：Foam Spray Cleaner The no-rinse foaming formula deeply cleans while leaving behind a fresh, clean finish. Just spray, wait, and wipe — no need for rinsing, saving you time and effort.
【Easy to Use – Quick Cleaning in Minutes】：Achieve spotless results in just 5–15 minutes. Simply spray the surface, let it work, then wipe away stains and grime effortlessly.
【Multipurpose Kitchen Degreaser – Works Everywhere】：Perfect for use on stovetops, cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and more. Leaves your entire kitchen looking fresh, sparkling, and brand new.
description: Capacity: 100ml Features: Our kitchen foam cleaner contains disodium EDTA, sodium bicarbonate, laureth-7. It can powerfully remove dirt and easily remove stubborn stains; the formula is mild and harmless to hands or objects; it is suitable for multiple purposes and can be used on various forsurfaces; the fragrance is fresh and the fragrance lasts after use. It is very simple to use: 1. Shake the bottle and spray evenly on the place that needs to be cleaned; 2. Wipe back and forth to make the stain disappear, and finally rinse with clean water. Multifunctional formula, quickly removes stubborn grease in the kitchen and makes the forsurface look brand new. Harmless to hands, no irritating odor, safer to use Products include: 1pcs kitchen foam cleaner, 2pcs kitchen foam cleaner Note: Please allow slight size errors (1~2 cm/0.39~0.78 inches) due to manual measurement, which is subject to the actual received; please allow slight errors in color under different monitors.
